{"tid":2127266,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"科大雷鼎鳴：特朗普不能連任","createTime":"2020-07-27T08:40:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-27T09:26:51.000Z","uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d861a0ba8d8e2e3a9e51f030f253121d50bf2a7f","tid":2127266,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T08:40:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://image2.stheadline.com/f/1500p0/0x0/100/hd/c2189383b1b9ba9a0bf7557efe202ec6/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200726/_2020072618485142714.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage2.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F1500p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fhd%2Fc2189383b1b9ba9a0bf7557efe202ec6%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200726%2F_2020072618485142714.jpg&h=9b63788b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n科技大學經濟學系前系主任雷鼎鳴今日接受電台節目訪問時指，香港屬美國地緣戰爭策略之一，相信隨著疫情控制不力，美國會繼續擴大與中國抗衡局面，本港亦會受到相當影響，雖然內地經濟復蘇迅速，有正面動力將本港從谷底拉出，惟香港面對很多負面因素，經濟前景不容樂觀。<br />\n<br />\n雷鼎鳴指，香港明顯成為美國行動步伐之一，他解釋，本港是其地緣戰爭一部分，如果香港多動亂或經濟金融受損，可被視向中方壓制手段，再加上美國大選在即，總統特朗普研判中美關係及局勢後，遂將矛頭指向中國，疫情控制愈差，愈需和中國抗衡。雷又指，距離美國大選尚餘100日，今屆政府形同跛腳鴨，預料特朗普不會成功連任。"},{"pid":"c5d81aa26a199271bdd7f35f5db5eb35da7741ff","tid":2127266,"uid":194326,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T08:41:02.000Z","msg":"又係呢條9up佬"},{"pid":"d16f841e9104646e7de362b92c8065e0c810bb86","tid":2127266,"uid":53959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T08:41:30.000Z","msg":"雷狗又出黎燈"},{"pid":"09d76f6a7bdc9dbae449b5afe0572fa09a53b239","tid":2127266,"uid":335434,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T08:53:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://miro.medium.com/max/1800/0*n6HxDzjs6gmRrdzm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmiro.medium.com%2Fmax%2F1800%2F0%2An6HxDzjs6gmRrdzm.png&h=2f61e5f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有雷嗚燈大力加持 呢次侵連任穩撚陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"651865d2c43c813d2f7cd68df85a982d13694021","tid":2127266,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote"